{
  "stem": "11133.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was at that point that my parents decided-- we-- well, they went back, really, to see if there was anybody left from the family.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And since there was nobody left from the family that we knew of, they let my uncle know, in Israel, and also my uncle in the United States, that we survived.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my parents decided Poland was not the place to stay.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was in school for about four weeks, just September.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in October, we smuggled over the border, out of Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And already at that point, Poland was closing its borders.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we smuggled in a Russian truck into Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And from Bratislava, we made our way into Prague-- back to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And from Prague, we went-- we waited there for about a week and a half, and then we were taken over the border-- the German-Czech border.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In the middle of the night, we walked across.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We missed the-- we made it through the Czech, but didn't quite make it behind the border of the Americans, but they let us in.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we made it into Hof, and from Hof into Landsberg, the displaced persons camp, where we stayed for a little while.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then into Mindelheim, where we stayed for a year and a half, and then the United States.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
